e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"係呢個post見到都係好知足既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"有時都唔知係知足 定係 升唔到上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過<br />\n<em><ins>從無求到渴求 <br />\n直到渴求整個宇宙<br />\n來到最後卻只想得救<br />\n忙著擁有 <br />\n忘掉你我本都一無所有</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n濕爬都講得岩  其實既然本身都係咩都冇 姐係家陣有既野就係讚左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"自己覺得富足，升唔升上去又有咩所謂，你已經存在係自己既理想生活中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9017ba3ca71677300b31d96c2fa928fc341e65ab","tid":1995234,"uid":80662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T11:51:28.000Z","msg":"有健康，有屋企人同老婆<br />\n依個時勢同老婆仲有穩定收入同工作<br />\n各自有樓有車有租收<br />\n各自有自己興趣同愛好<br />\n<br />\n唔算好有錢<br />\n但一定唔駛捱苦<br />\n<br />\n做人做到咁仲想要求乜<br />\n<br />\n我知足架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddbb620c99fe15d7cd07307842b3eeffab6ce36","tid":1995234,"uid":255286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"有幾好既呀媽家姐細佬細妹<br />\n唔有錢 但衣食住行冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係sen生  係有d不足  但足夠入八大醫療科<br />\n返pt中意左個靚仔上司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後一齊左 宜家一年幾  <br />\n佢勁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我太hea gpa得2都無人照肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使疫情持續家姐滯留喺外國 <br />\n我都仲有pt返 可以養細佬妹同家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男朋友見我得返好少錢 呢2個月拍拖食飯佢請晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讀大學識到好好朋友 大家都唔八婆而係毒絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生活固然有唔如意 <br />\n但好多細微既好事就足夠抵消<br />\n所以我要多d將呢份祝福傳俾其他人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}